
Install
=======

Hemera depends on the following libraries:

 * ply 2.3 (or superior)
 * pygraphviz (or superior)

Ply:

The ply library is easy to install, the library can be founded in lib subdirectory.

Pygraphviz:

We followed the procedure discribed in:

http://groups.google.com/group/pygraphviz-discuss/browse_thread/thread/f3b385409bb66420?pli=1

Basically, we downloaded the pygraphviz package from:
http://networkx.lanl.gov/download/pygraphviz/

And the graphviz package from:
http://graphviz.org/pub/graphviz/development/macos/leopard/

Finnaly, we edited the setup.py from the pygraphviz adding the correct location of libraries:

$ diff setup.py setup.py~ 
47,50d46
< # Mac OS X (pkg from ATT)
< library_path='/usr/local/lib'
< include_path='/usr/local/include/graphviz'


Pendente
========

1. Mostrar o sequent inicial antes de limpar os goals.

2. Melhorar parser para casos como "a --> a --> a" e aceitar apenas
formulas bem formadas, não aceitar partes de formulas, como no caso "a
-> a" que ele aceita o "a".


Distribuição
============

python setup.py sdist


Instalação
==========

Requer Python 2.4.3 ou superior. Bibliotecas python necessárias no diretório lib:

 * ply 2.3 (ou superior)
 * pygraphviz (0.34 ou superior)

Ambas as bibliotecas são instaladas com o comando:

python setup.py install

